title: They appeared in deepfake porn videos without their consent. Few laws protect them.
description: Manipulated pornography featuring the faces of nonconsenting victims like QTCinderella is becoming more pervasive online.

title: Congress has had a hands-off approach to Big Tech. Will the AI arms race be any different?
description: Congress has balked at regulating Big Tech companies. But with AI and ChatGPT, some tech-savvy lawmakers are pushing Congress to step in.
